CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Flash Newspicture Magazine, November 1, 1938, pg. 11, reads: "Throughout the county the Young Men's Christian Association is launching drives to increase the membership of their association. In Pittsburg [sic] PA.,.. ...Holding trophy (right) is winner Dr. R. W. Taylor who produced the most cash money in contest."
TitMainTitle: Dr. R. W. Taylor holding trophy, for YMCA membership drive, in Centre Avenue YMCA
